Name: Citation needed
Body: Some of the information contained in this post requires additional references. Please edit to add citations to reliable sources that support the assertions made here. Unsourced material may be disputed or deleted.

Name: Current event
Body: Post is related to a rapidly changing event.

Name: Insufficient explanation
Body: We're looking for long answers that provide some explanation and context. Don't just give a one-line answer; explain why your answer is right, ideally with citations. Answers that don't include explanations may be removed.

Name: Current answers are outdated
Body: The current answer(s) are out-of-date and require revision given recent changes.

Name: Draw attention
Body: This question has not received enough attention.

Name: Improve details
Body: The current answers do not contain enough detail.

Name: Authoritative reference needed
Body: Looking for an answer drawing from credible and/or official sources.

Name: Canonical answer required
Body: The question is widely applicable to a large audience. A detailed canonical answer is required to address all the concerns.

Name: Reward existing answer
Body: One or more of the answers is exemplary and worthy of an additional bounty.

Name: Content dispute
Body: This post has been locked while disputes about its content are being resolved. For more info [visit meta]($MetaUrl).

Name: Offtopic comments
Body: This post has been locked due to the high amount of off-topic comments generated. For extended discussions, please use [chat]($ChatUrl).

Name: Historical significance
Body:
This question exists because it has historical significance, but **it is not considered a good, on-topic question for this site**, 
so please do not use it as evidence that you can ask similar questions here.  This question and its answers are frozen and cannot be changed.
More info: [help].

Name: Wiki Answer
Body: This question's answers are a collaborative effort: if you see something that can be improved, just edit the answer to improve it! *No additional answers can be added here*
